#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:5
msgid "3D Cursor"
msgstr "3D游标"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:7
msgid ""
"The 3D Cursor is a point in 3D space which can be used for a number of purposes."
msgstr "3D游标是三维空间中的一个点，可用于多种用途。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:11
msgid "Placement"
msgstr "定位"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:13
msgid "There are a few methods to position the 3D cursor."
msgstr "有几种方法可以定位3D游标。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:17
msgid "Direct Placement with the Mouse"
msgstr "用鼠标直接放置"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:22
msgid "Positioning the 3D cursor with two orthogonal views."
msgstr "用两个正交视图定位3D游标。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:24
msgid ""
"Enable the cursor tool. Using :kbd:`RMB` in the 3D View will place the 3D "
"cursor directly under your mouse pointer."
msgstr "启用游标工具。在3D视图中使用 :kbd:`RMB` 将把3D游标直接放在鼠标指针下。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:27
msgid "The view space is used to control the rotation of the 3D Cursor."
msgstr "3D游标用于视图空间旋转的控制。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:29
msgid ""
"For accuracy you should use two perpendicular orthogonal 3D Views, i.e. any "
"combination of top :kbd:`Numpad7`, front :kbd:`Numpad1` and side :kbd:"
"`Numpad3`. That way you can control the positioning along two axes in one view "
"and determine depth in the second view."
msgstr ""
"对于精确定位，需使用两个垂直的正交3D视图，如顶视图 ( :kbd:`Numpad7` ), 前视图 "
"( :kbd:`Numpad1` ) 和侧视图 ( :kbd:`Numpad3` ).这样, 你可以在一个视图中沿两个坐"
"标轴控制定位, 并在第二个视图中确定深度。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:34
msgid ""
"By default the depth of the geometry under the cursor is used, this can be "
"disabled using the *Cursor Surface Project* toggle in the :doc:`Preferences </"
"editors/preferences/editing>`."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下3D游标可定位于几何体表面。在 :doc:`设置 </editors/preferences/"
"editing>` 中启用 *游标表面投影* 选项切换禁用此功能。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:40
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Snap Menu </scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/snap>` "
"which allows the cursor placement relative to scene objects."
msgstr ""
":doc:`吸附菜单 </scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/snap>` 允许游标相"
"对于场景物体放置。"

